last_episode_to_air.name: Could it be magic?
last_episode_to_air.overview: Entering the last hour, one of the comedians is still not 100% sure of the rules. Another is struggling to get enough attention but is not ready to give up. There will be a workout, there will be red cards, and there will be rock. But who will be the winner?

name: LOL: Last One Laughing Norway
original_name: LOL: Den som ler sist - Norge
overview: Sigrid Bonde Tusvik gathers ten of Norway's funniest people in the same room, with the following challenge: Don't laugh for six hours, while you do whatever it takes to make the others laugh. The winner of LOL: Den som ler sist leaves the house with NOK 100,000 for their chosen charity.

episodes.name: Don't do it, Maria
episodes.overview: There's both joy and fear as the comedians greet each other, realizing the impossible task they're about to face. Host Sigrid sets off the competition, and everyone enters survival mode from the get-go. The first White Joker Card is played, with several unexpected consequences.

episodes.name: Drinking tequila from the senioritas shoe
episodes.overview: A love of wigs leads to a downfall. One comedian experiences a severe loss of self-esteem as another one gets loud. A surprise guest leads to chaos and a shocking exit. A White Joker card reveals a hidden childhood dream and showcases a questionable ballet.

episodes.name: The rude carol of the bells
episodes.overview: It's half-time, and the comedians realize they must raise the stakes, resulting in four white Joker cards being played out. Will a rude song be enough to draw out the giggles? Or will a sad poem do the trick? How about some pantomime? One comedian's struggle to understand the rules might prove fatal.

episodes.name: The ship comes loaded
episodes.overview: A surprisingly vulgar boat show proves too much for some, and Sigrid sees the need to confiscate a bothersome doll. A comedian is subjected to plagiarism, and there's a sigh of relief when a strong contender is forced to exit the competition.

episodes.name: The Flamenco Duel
episodes.overview: A Black Joker Card threatens to backfire, while another turns a recipe for Pasta Bolognese into an unexpected comedy nightmare. Two comedians go head-to-head in a surprising musical battle. A White Joker Card provides the contestants with a self-defense class that hardly proves a great defense against laughter. A surprise guest makes matters worse.
